values:
...through the years...
i've conquered my fears,
wiped away my tears,
and slowly opened up my ears...
...discovering things i never really knew...
...and each & everyday, u found otu something new...
...then there were times when i only understood a few...
but that never really made me feel blue!!!
instead, it made me try harder...
to study and study because knowledge is power!!!

...i like you but i don't know you...
and because of that, i feel truly blue...
...i really wish i could get the chance to know you...
...because when that day comes,
it would be a dream come true...
hi! i'm dianne...wow...this, i think, would be a beginning of something great...really, really great... :P
